export default <svg id="calendar-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22">
  <rect id="Rectangle_6" data-name="Rectangle 6" width="22" height="22" fill="none"/>
  <rect id="Rectangle_7" data-name="Rectangle 7" width="16" height="15" rx="1" transform="translate(3 3)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="1.5"/>
  <line id="Line_1" data-name="Line 1" y2="2" transform="translate(15 2)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="1.5"/>
  <line id="Line_2" data-name="Line 2" y2="2" transform="translate(7 2)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="1.5"/>
  <line id="Line_3" data-name="Line 3" x2="16" transform="translate(3 7)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="1.5"/>
  <g id="Calander_Dates" data-name="Calander Dates" transform="translate(6 10)">
    <rect id="Rectangle_8" data-name="Rectangle 8" width="2" height="2" fill="currentColor"/>
    <rect id="Rectangle_9" data-name="Rectangle 9" width="2" height="2" transform="translate(3)" fill="currentColor"/>
    <rect id="Rectangle_10" data-name="Rectangle 10" width="2" height="2" transform="translate(3 3)" fill="currentColor"/>
    <rect id="Rectangle_11" data-name="Rectangle 11" width="2" height="2" transform="translate(6 3)" fill="currentColor"/>
  </g>
</svg>
